name: Must See Eat Street Markets, Followed by a View of Brisbane City
description: We will start the night out Brisbane's must do Eat Street Markets where all children under 12 have free entry. You are free to wonder, eat and enjoy Eat Street until you are ready to move onto our next activity. The next activity brings you to one of Brisbane's most beautiful spot by the river where you can enjoy our ride on our famous wheel. After that we have a lovely walk along the river, ending the night looking out over the river.
